Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my dad's job, my mom and sisters moved overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so starting this spring, I started living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my first time living alone lasted only a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rikka. I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, already. We start school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I attempted to keep my dark chuunibyou history hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and start life over again in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,just like I did last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Rikka here foiled me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to awaken, Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, True Eye of the Evil King! The time of awakening has come!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,I wanna fall in love.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,盗汗夢が続く
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,約束しても、心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,一人じゃないって　信じたいのに
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,思い続けてるだけで　幸せなんて言えないね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,虚ろな自信　背負っていても　君が笑う
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,そして私の勇気になる
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,一つの言葉で君の世界を変えられたら、
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,二つの恋が進化する
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,本当だよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,巡らせた迷いが見つけた答えはいつでも君に導かれた
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,届ける覚悟が様にならなくても素直に伝えたい
