Comment: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:08.51,TL,,0,0,0,,I wanna fall in love
Comment: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.48,TL,,0,0,0,,The nightmares continue
Comment: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.05,TL,,0,0,0,,Even with our promise, there's fear in my heart
Comment: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.05,TL,,0,0,0,,I really want to believe that I'm not alone
Comment: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:42.65,TL,,0,0,0,,Just thinking can't be called happiness
Comment: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:48.86,TL,,0,0,0,,Even though you lack self-confidence, you smile
Comment: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.81,TL,,0,0,0,,So become my courage
Comment: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:57.25,TL,,0,0,0,,When one word can change your world
Comment: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.77,TL,,0,0,0,,Both of our loves will evolve
Comment: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.32,TL,,0,0,0,,That's the truth
Comment: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:07.24,TL,,0,0,0,,When confusion surrounded me
Comment: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:11.14,TL,,0,0,0,,The answer always led to you
Comment: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:15.85,TL,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm never prepared to tell you
Comment: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.35,TL,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know
Comment: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:21.11,TL,,0,0,0,,My voice glistens with the contents of my heart
Comment: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:26.94,TL,,0,0,0,,With the voice, it echoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka, is sunny side up okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dark side up," please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunny side up" it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her too many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the ribbon for my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Was it them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to prepare it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a busy time! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.56,OS,,0,0,0,,Note: {\i1}ahoge{\i0} is literally idiot hair, a slim forelock of hair that sticks straight up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your {\i1}ahoge{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It's my "charm point"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This spring, Rikka's mother also had to move out of town for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...which meant Rikka had to live on her own too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Rikka's baggage being moved out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they finally made their move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Her grandfather accidentally terminated the contract on their apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll have to live with me until you've settled on a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency Code: Triple Four activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Rikka came to live with me temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be woken up by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See it from my point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.93,OS,,0,0,0,,The Priestess wouldn't be okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to Touka-san and told her I found Rikka an apartment for her alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've been keeping up this facade for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera, I give you my demonic fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting used to these red fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it a little try. They're as good as strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming more and more like the Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you under her influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The fluid! The green, squishy matter is attacking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stay perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wiping at it will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to dab at it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:43.34,OS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're heading out, please do take a collapsible umbrella with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dating, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get to romance if it has to be concealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even had a normal girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...so having a first girlfriend with chunibyo will be even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Things settled down in a way that isn't much different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shinka Nibutani, and I'm in the 11th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,High school two syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what you promised yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the hieroglyphs, the hateful magic barrier attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,triggered by the Freemasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our uninvited guests the unfathomable parallel world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean our discussion about performing the Schrodinger's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cat experiment using Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Never! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. How we're living together at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only thing I spoke to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We should visit the real estate agent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are referring to my new base, it has already been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the demon world of the impossibly Wicked One,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible to mere mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your antenna hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you lovebirds are already at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Isshiki. Makoto Isshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! The guy in the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who sacrificed everything for upperclassman Kumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the crew cut guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Crew Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me that! That version of me is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at my Rock'n'Roll head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki, what happened to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go visit the student councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting it all wrong, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair type changed when it grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kumin-senpai! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka-chan and Togashi-kun. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both 11th graders today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're a 12th grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. And it's such a let-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'll have to study for university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, that isn't what I mean. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because 12th grade is sooo next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it told me to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? I want to make everyone laugh just like how Morisummer-chan did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing older brings many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning! What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am wearing normal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"How do you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you experiencing advanced senility?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, if I might have a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.83,OS,,0,0,0,,DEKO DEKO MIDDLE MIDDLE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, let's make this another spirited school year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a lot of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but my second year will be completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will claw my way to the top of this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}The next speech comes from our new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}...represented by Dekomori Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I am the new student representative, Sanae Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}With the warm days of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}...the trees become enrobed in fresh, new green livery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that she got better grades than you had last year, Nibutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Our student lives also begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Deko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe everyone knows that there are white and black worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seeing spirits requires the proper heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love is everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, Nibutani-san has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We share the same class once again, Light Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Takanashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanase-sensei is our home room teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They told to get my hair cut for school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd know? This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are we in the same class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in Class 3 next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that relief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You made no attempt to hide your relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi-kun, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Togashi's friend? I'm Nibutani—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Pot, meet kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only bringing this up because we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Tatenashi-san not to mention our middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,memories at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I pondered all summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I pondered about going to this high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really intend to spend three years of my life in that loser's club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant to True Eye of the Evil King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,User of the Mjolnir Hammer, Sanae Dekomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...is hereby reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the deviously devious Fake Morisummer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,would dare stage an attack on me in my temporary guise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now observe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I spin right left, and left right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposing revolutions shall produce a kink between dimensions and space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And by adding an additional revolution, I shall produce unlimited power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! The Mjolnir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have weak semicircular canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori will not be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.00,OS,,0,0,0,,Rich Cheese (6 pcs)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're such an energetic First Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a reward, I will give you the cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,love. So. Much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One must deal with trouble of one's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Paging a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the staff room immediately. I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,please report to the staff room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The school has been overrun by terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing. The school mailed at least three to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They all came back returned to sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be due to the fact that my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,existence had been erased from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When we phone you, it says that number is not in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My existence had been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you exist right now, so perhaps it'll go through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye! My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.94,OS,,0,0,0,,Far-East Magical Napping Society - Summer Thereof
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to buy it, but at this rate, it'll get ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just try to take a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here and sit down with us, Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The incubus lives in that coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one forged in the darkness such as I dare not approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I once experienced a frightening dream while under its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What did you dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, the light! The Light Being is paralyzing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that in the form of a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to choose, where would you want to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What we were talking just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your base and battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the base, where the True Eye of the Evil King and the Dark Flame Master demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That base where the magical magnetic field is also the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that idiot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what she did to my costume for Theatre Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.54,OS,,0,0,0,,PERMANENT MARKER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to search for a new base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For all that...
