Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(1234,384)}Sunlight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(1263,505)}Air
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(171,61)}Real Estate Worker Kabu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(955,155)}Real Estate Worker Kabu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where you should set up house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(568,260)}Real Estate Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(752,284)}Apartments, Units
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(769,219)}Room Searching
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz-1\fs20\pos(1044,324)}No Bicycle Parking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I desire a underground labyrinth. With an ancient castle is also okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposite the convenience store, there's a castle with "British Parliament" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You definitely can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't realize how expensive rent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I knew it might be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know much about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I transfer to a new base, will I still be able to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I go to and from school, I won't even come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably will turn out to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to go to your room to report activity in the magical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be good if you don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop by to pick you up for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for a place that we can play at and is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Takana-san's apartment has become empty. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you move, Rikka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give me an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Touka...-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite departing for Italy soon, you won't give me your new home's address. Nor answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's become of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you are mistaken, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You are maintaining state of being an unable to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to chase Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This servant Dekomori, will buy you time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Masters, please evacuate to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize who you're up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the priestess who, in a previous batle once force-fed Dekomori a mass of rotten dairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wish for a worthier opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Your hand! Your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,IDIOT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your intent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! This is- this is Fake Morisummer's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying! It your fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori deeply respects you, Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As my master's sister, I am at your command!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to throw me under the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume positions and prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Burst open, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanishment This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She easily deflected master's Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,LO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,LOV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,LOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,LOVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a physical attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.04,OS,,0,0,0,,(DEMON GOD GUN) MA SHIN GAN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwarz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrostire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's arrostire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "oven roasted."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You shacked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're living together as boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please control your disgusting imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the one with the dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what? I, Dekomori, am always pure of thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone beet red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For a little kid, you have a really dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet, you big-boobed freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shacking is sooo shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's really not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that a full grown boy like yourself had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,....but to shack up with my little sister with whom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you are in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You dissolved your pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dumped whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it! I'm saying we are not "shacking up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's mostly because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,concerned about leaving Rikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been almost a week now, and nothing of the sort is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract remains unaltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're not "living together"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's it! We're roommates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a home share situation. You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that logic will fly by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I will permit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you cannot live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find her an apartment. If you have a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will take Rikka to Italy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical society! The Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I to be imprisoned in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy is home to the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vatican, Sixth Sense, I see dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Home to the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzuha, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you were told I was coming back for the new school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been living together with Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she doesn't have her own place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of rooms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I felt uneasy about Rikka living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would act as supervisor, it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please let her stay here just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my life alone with Rikka came to an abrupt end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.33,OS,,0,0,0,,TOGASHI MAIL FOR NAKANISHI HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...and three teenagers began life together in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta's notebook. I forgot to return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone new move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She never was able to get her apartment back.
